<div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="text-center jumbotron">
    <h1>Science is all about you</h1>
  
    <h2>
      Guide, support and engage science by participating in scientific studies.
      <br>
      And earn some <span class="highlight">$$</span> along the way!
    </h2>
  
    <%= link_to "Sign up for free", signup_path, class: "btn btn-lg btn-primary" %>
    <%= link_to "Explore science labs", '#', class: "btn btn-lg btn-primary" %>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
      <div id="featured-lab">
        <div class="featured-heading">
          <span class="lab-label">Featured lab:</span> <a href="http://www.hbs.edu/behave/">Computer Lab for Experimental Research</a>
        </div>
        <div><span class="lab-label">Organization:</span> <a href="http://www.hbs.edu">Harvard Business School</a></div>
        <div><span class="lab-label">Participant location:</span> Boston, MA</div>
        <div>
          <span class="lab-label">About the lab:</span>
          The Computer Lab for Experimental Research (CLER) studies human behavior 
          and decision-making by inviting participants from across the Boston area. 
          We pay participants $15-25 per session to take part in lab-based studies 
          that contribute to this cutting-edge research.
        </div>
        <div>
          <%= link_to "Learn more", '#', class: "btn btn-lg btn-primary" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


<div class="container" id="descriptive-section">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col">
        <h1>Why participate?</h1>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
            <div><%= image_tag("lab-smiley-beakers.svg", alt: "StudyMe.Science logo", class: "lab-smiley") %></div>
            <div>
              <h2>Be a part of the scientific process!</h2>
              <p>Your participation in scientific studies makes them possible,
                and it guides science towards the right answers.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
            <div><%= image_tag("lab-smiley-dollars.svg", alt: "StudyMe.Science logo", class: "lab-smiley") %></div>
            <div>
              <h2>Earn a few extra bucks!</h2>
              <p>While it won't make you a millionaire, many studies pay for your participation.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
            <div><%= image_tag("lab-smiley-book.svg", alt: "StudyMe.Science logo", class: "lab-smiley") %></div>
            <div>
              <h2>Learn and engage with your scientific community!</h2>
              <p>See firsthand how scientific studies are conducted. 
                Witness cutting edge research. Get to know your local
                science labs. Most researchers welcome your questions about
                their research!</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
</div>